snippet.title: Game Play Preview - Sentinels of the Multiverse: The Video Game
snippet.description:
Check out this first look at gameplay for the upcoming Sentinels of the Multiverse: The Video Game. 

Sentinels of the Multiverse: The Video Game is coming to Android tablets and iPad in Fall 2014! 

Want to hear more about Handelabra or Sentinels of the Multiverse? We've got you covered. 
http://sentinelsdigital.com/
http://handelabra.com/forums
http://twitter.com/handelabra
http://facebook.com/handelabra


For more info on the card game created by Greater Than Games: 
http://sentinelsofthemultiverse.com
https://greaterthangames.com
